      en: ["4 small baguettes or demi-baguettes (about 20 cm each), halved lengthwise", "400 g pork tenderloin, thinly sliced (about 5 mm)", "2 tbsp soy sauce", "1 tbsp fish sauce", "1 tsp sesame oil + 1 tsp sugar + 1/4 tsp black pepper (marinade)", "2 medium carrots (about 200 g), peeled and julienned", "100 g daikon, peeled and julienned (or extra carrot)", "3 tbsp rice vinegar", "1 tbsp sugar + 1/2 tsp fine salt (for pickling)", "60 g chicken liver pâté", "4 tbsp mayonnaise", "1 large cucumber, cut into thin batons", "2 jalapeños or red chillies, thinly sliced", "20 g fresh coriander, sprigs"],
